  <text>
    <body>
      <head>Nevermore</head>
      <p>
        <l>There's no living in my life anymore</l>
        <l>The seas have gone dry and the rain stopped falling</l>
        <l>Please don't you cry anymore</l>
        <l>Can't you see</l>
        <l>Listen to the breeze, whisper to me please</l>
        <l>Don't send me to the path of nevermore</l>
      </p>
      <p>
        <l>Even the valleys below</l>
        <l>Where the rays of the sun were so warm and tender</l>
        <l>Now haven't anything to grow</l>
        <l>Can't you see</l>
        <l>Why did you have to leave me</l>
        <l>Why did you deceive me</l>
        <l>You send me to the path of nevermore</l>
        <l>When you say you didn't love me anymore</l>
        <l>Nevermore</l>
        <l>Nevermore</l>
      </p>
    </body>
